'''萊斯里·尼爾森'''（{{lang-en|Leslie William Nielsen}}, [[加拿大勳章|OC]]，{{bd|1926年|2月11日|2010年|11月28日|catIdx=Nielsen, Leslie}}）是[[加拿大裔美國人|加拿大-美國]][[艾美獎|艾美獎]]提名[[喜劇演員|喜劇演員]]與[[電影演員|電影演員]]。他著名的電影角色為《-{[[白頭神探|白頭神探]]}-》的探長法蘭克（Frank Drebin），《[[空前絕後滿天飛|空前絕後滿天飛]]》裡的盧馬克（Dr. Rumack）與在《[[驚聲尖笑|驚聲尖笑]]》系列電影裡的[[總統|總統]]哈里斯（Harris）。

尼爾森出生於[[加拿大|加拿大]]。小時候與母親曾遭父親家暴而逃家，二戰前服役於加拿大皇家空軍擔任航空砲手，但因為年紀太小未被派往海外。退伍後曾短暫擔任DJ，之後拿獎學金學習戲劇並搬往紐約展開演藝生涯。萊斯里·尼爾森有一位哥哥艾瑞克1980年代曾擔任加拿大副首相。2010年11月28日助理表示，尼爾森因[[肺炎|肺炎]]治療，在住處[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]附近的醫院去世，享壽84歲。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.rti.org.tw/index_newsContent.aspx?nid=269790&id=3&id2=2|title=笑彈龍虎榜喜劇演員尼爾森去世 享壽84歲|date=2010-11-28|publisher=中央廣播電台|accessdate=2010-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101202031429/http://news.rti.org.tw/index_newsContent.aspx?nid=269790&id=3&id2=2|archive-date=2010-12-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
<!-- Although Nielsen's acting career crossed a variety of genres in both television and movies, he has achieved his greatest film success in comedies, including ''Airplane!'' and ''The Naked Gun'' series of films. His portrayal of serious characters seemingly oblivious of (and complicit in) their absurd surroundings gave Nielsen a reputation as a comedian.<ref name="NYT">{{cite web | title=nytimes.com| work=A Fall Guy as Antihero | url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=940DE3DE153DF931A35751C1A96E948260| accessmonthday=April 16 | accessyear=2007}}</ref> A series of later comedies attempted to emulate the popularity of his prior roles.

This paralleled the serious roles of his early career. Leading roles in the science fiction classic ''[[Forbidden_Planet|Forbidden Planet]]'' and as the ship's captain in ''[[The_Poseidon_Adventure_(film)|The Poseidon Adventure]]'' came long before Nielsen considered a turn to comedy. His deadpan delivery as a doctor in 1980's ''Airplane!'' marked a turning point in Nielsen's career, one that would make him, in the words of movie critic [[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]], "the [[Laurence_Olivier|Olivier]] of spoofs."<ref name="Ebert">{{cite web | title=RogerEbert.com| work=Scary Movie 3 | url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20031024/REVIEWS/310240305/1023| accessmonthday=April 4 | accessyear=2007}}</ref> -->

